ney U test). The rapid MERS-CoV nucleocapsid protein detection assay is able to rapidly detect lineage C betacoronaviruses in bats. It detected significantly more Ty-BatCoV-HKU4 than Pi-BatCoV-HKU5 because MERS-CoV is more closely related to Ty-BatCoV-HKU4 than Pi-BatCoV-HKU5. This assay will facilitate rapid on-site mass screening of animal samples for ancestors of MERS-CoV and tracking transmission in the related bat species.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Woo, Patrick C. Y.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Lau, Susanna K. P.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Chen, Yixin", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Wong, Emily Y. M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Chan, Kwok-Hung", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Chen, Honglin", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Zhang, Libiao", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Xia, Ningshao", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Yuen, Kwok-Yung", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Animals", "Chiroptera", "Coronavirus Infections", "Middle East Respiratory Syndrome Coronavirus", "Phylogeny", "Spike Glycoprotein, Coronavirus", "Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/3b44ef0519d3c2d5bf6a9882c53a4c39", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/dcef939cb534451c67de7e7737ace1918778f4f0f6c4648fc6786d4661b6a7c5", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/E98R9225", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/E98R9225", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/53fb1cebf5c945fe4ed2984b5b9361a2!/b292443-295657", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type"